<h1>Accomodation</h1>
		  <p align="justify">
The conference main venue is the <a href="http://en.sanmartin.si/"> Hotel San Martin</a>.

The hotel is exclusively reserved for the conference, and it will accomodate a large number of the participants in twenty-six rooms. 
</p>
<p>
The price for six nights, including breakfasts, 6 lunches, and 4 dinners is 650 euros for occupancy and 550 euros for double occupancy.

This price includes the social dinner, two excursions, and a wine tasting session. The hotel has one of the best cellars in the area, with thousands of different bottles.
</p>
<p>
<b>Registration to the meeting is complete only after the hotel reservation will be made. </b> You can book your room contacting the hotel by email at  and mentioning that you are coming for the cosmology conference.
     </p>
 <p>      
Other accomodation is availabe at 
     </p>
